{"tid":1218992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先TBB新聞︰美國田納西州爆發警民衝突，最少25人受傷，主要是警員及記者","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T18:43:22.000Z","uid":46356,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9b2b1201a23ce3c32a8301853ec854c0198fd3","tid":1218992,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"美國田納西州爆發警民衝突，<span style=\"color: brown;\">最少25人受傷，主要是警員及記者</span>。<br />\n<br />\n大批警察戴上頭盔和手持盾牌戒備。事發在孟菲斯市，當地周三晚上十一點，民眾向警員擲石及磚頭，有在場採訪的記者亦被波及，多輛警車和附近建築物損毀，警方一度施放催淚氣體驅趕群眾。<br />\n<br />\n觸發今次警民衝突是由於有執法人員到北部一個社區執行搜查令，警方指，涉案21歲男子拒捕，又涉嫌駕車多次撞向警車，之後再持武器走出車外，警員開了十多槍將他擊斃。事件引發當地居民不滿，觸發衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5d024c46e60383eb0792ec8e/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5d024c46e60383eb0792ec8e%2F&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e1c68600\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5d024c46e60383eb0792ec8e/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都幾煞有介事咁去報"},{"pid":"676c8ec2f472bcebf96639144b41e695cbf4e1fb","tid":1218992,"uid":169074,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"446aa92fda968020c33cd12aedcc95e3125ea8e7","tid":1218992,"uid":14449,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"美國田納西州爆發<span style=\"color: red;\">警民衝突</span>，最少25人受傷，主要是警員及記者。<br />\n呢d就叫警民衝突，我地就暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c5984c1492b8d6e80d9eb7c809962a99321805","tid":1218992,"uid":19287,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"香港玻璃都冇爛一塊已經叫暴動"},{"pid":"46943e1a7118e1997c5f8829aa5a192c92be1710","tid":1218992,"uid":79181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:29:40.000Z","msg":"多輛警車和附近建築物損毀<br />\n警蓄望唔望到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aced1dbea4d